n common injuries like car accidents slip and falls or workplace illnesses what is a statute of limitations the law limits the amount of time you can file a claim and collect damages for your auto accident that law is called the statute of limitations no matter how great your loss you will not be able to collect if you miss this deadline your lawyer will know all the deadlines for your state putting a claim together can take time so its important to consult with a lawyer near you as soon as possible some accidents and injuries our lawyers can help with accident types sideswipe collisions tbone collisions headon collisions multivehicle pileups vehicle rollover vehicle types car accidents truck accidents motorcycle accidents bus accidents nonfatal injuries whiplash injuries back and neck injuries herniated discs broken bones head trauma and concussions serious injuries coma spinal cord injuries traumatic brain injuries fatality how much is my claim worth about first injury help we run a free nationwide service that connects you with top injury attorneys servicing your area your injury is a priority and should be treated with great care and compassion our network of lawyers are skilled in winning the most money for injury victims we understand that you need compensation to get your life back on track the process  free consultation speak to an attorney without obligation no fee unless you win if you dont win you dont pay maximize your settlement get experienced help for your injury free nationwide service nationwide legal help service since  close free claim evaluation  first injury help firstinjuryhelp  complete injured in a car accident how much is your claim worth lets see if you may qualify what type of injury did you suffer  select one  car accident injury workplace injury personal injury medical malpractice approximate date of injury month jan feb mar apr may jun jul aug sep oct nov dec year continue please tell us a little about the injury are you the person who 